{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras/All_images_with_logo.png?t=1739418250\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Geyserlands </i>is a deck-building game of modern otherworldly mystery. You are a newly\u00a0 assigned detective in a national park nobody knows exists.\u00a0 Level up your cards, grow your deck and explore intertwining stories.  Unlock secret powers and gain special advantages.  But delve too deep and <i>Geyserlands</i> will consume you.  How will your story end in <i>Geyserlands</i>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras/Steam_Text_Divider.png?t=1739418250\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect a deck from hundreds of cards that tell the story of your character's history, abilities, insights and connections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the cards you draw each turn to solve some of Geyserlands' hundreds of mysteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve mysteries to earn new and better cards and remove weaker cards from your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape despair and death with a variety of upgradable healing cards that prevent Geyserlands from consuming you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn strange powers and supernatural edges that allow you to push your luck and accomplish the impossible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel the secrets of Geyserlands.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However your story ends, you will gain new cards for your next journey.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3208570?t=1739418250","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackgroun